## Stack
Backend: Django 4 + Wagtail 6, PostgreSQL, Celery/Redis.  
Web: Vue 3 + Vite + Tailwind v4 + DaisyUI v5.  
Mobile: Expo SDK > 51, React Native + TypeScript.

## Directory map
backend/        → Django project “medguard_backend”  
frontend/       → Vite Vue app “medguard-frontend” 
mobile/         → Expo app “medguard-mobile” 
infra/          → Docker, CI, Terraform  
docs/           → Markdown & OpenAPI specs

## I18N
Supported locales: `en-ZA`, `af-ZA`. Use Django `LocaleMiddleware`; Vue I18n lazy-loads JSON; Expo uses `expo-localization`.  Strings **must** appear in translation files, never hard-coded.
